Operating System Lab3, part 1: Multi-producer Multi-consumer problem

To run it, go to the "producer-consumer" directory and type:

	make
	./main_producer_consumer [producer number] [consumer number] [max_sleep_seconds] [total_items2produce] [buffer_size]
	
Some information will be printed to the screen to tell you where the program
runs. 

At the end, the total number of items produced and consumed will be printed
to the screen, you can check the values to see the correctness of the program.
